{"tid":1029746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本土派學生動源、香港民族陣綫、香港獨立聯盟、港語學明辦「終結普教中制度暴力誓師大會」","createTime":"2019-02-20T12:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T13:07:04.000Z","uid":153615,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"efa4a3860349cc85bdb83c19fd92d602047580bb","tid":1029746,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPzkOMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPzkOMJ.png&h=76bd6df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日學童以普通話溝通情況近發關注，多個本土派團體明日（21 日）下午舉行「終結普教中制度暴力誓師大會」，批評普教中是制度暴力，違反兒童權利公約，促請國際社會關注。<br />\n<br />\n早前針對有學童在電視新聞訪問中稱，若在校講廣東話會被罰的事件，因不滿浸大普通話考試一度佔領學校語文中心的陳樂行，學生動源召集人鍾翰林、香港民族陣綫發言人梁頌恆、香港獨立聯盟召集人陳家駒等會到場，呼籲國際社會關注普教中的情況，交代「終結『普教中』制度暴力」的計劃。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BE%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E8%BE%A6-%E7%B5%82%E7%B5%90%E6%99%AE%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E8%AA%93%E5%B8%AB%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83/?fbclid=IwAR2f_8NBg6pbrd0nvUy2KDoOhsjM53_A_eW9nfnvsUFSYG9vA5B7SDy6InE#.XG1GGz83yoM.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%25AA%2593%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2f_8NBg6pbrd0nvUy2KDoOhsjM53_A_eW9nfnvsUFSYG9vA5B7SDy6InE%23.XG1GGz83yoM.facebook&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n83ejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=0b5fb0a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%25AA%2593%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%25A4%25A7